The paper deals with the construction of codes and their properties, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT). The paper also involves the study of multivariate polynomials and their restrictions, which is a topic in computational complexity (cs.CC) and data structures (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the trade-off between redundancy and locality, which is a topic in cryptography (cs.CR) and systems and control (cs.SI).
